WEBVTT

00:09.970 --> 00:11.792
Ah huh? Haa.

00:11.875 --> 00:14.958
Woah-ho-ho!

00:18.625 --> 00:19.570
Sanitler, değil mi?

00:20.720 --> 00:21.696
