00:22.004 --> 00:22.867
Naa. Mat sita.

00:23.271 --> 00:25.410
Casupa ti. Ova sa ta-ta.

00:25.680 --> 00:27.195
Bir baba si, ha?

00:27.284 --> 00:31.048
Esekita! Ah patika. A Zizi!

00:31.125 --> 00:35.333
Eh wana ayy. Eh sawa ti. A tita pata!

00:36.417 --> 00:37.667
