00:52.417 --> 00:53.833
Eh yo qure kara!

00:53.917 --> 00:55.625
Naygo siqe tacke.

00:57.818 --> 01:02.125
- Jo pa sa tava!
Ah, çok şaşırdım.

01:02.208 --> 01:03.458
Sepa da!

01:03.938 --> 01:05.750
Glorckling startrick!

01:05.830 --> 01:08.083
- Eh para kiri guratick.
- Se passa.

01:08.170 --> 01:11.000
- Katchu a ti-tat.
- Pfft, of.

01:11.083 --> 01:14.792
Eh sa "öh". B-- Batgar ve baroba, si?

01:14.880 --> 01:19.625
- "Ah, bak, eh patuse."
- "Toute houre."

01:19.709 --> 01:22.042
- "Ana ma kin a poura doura."

01:22.125 --> 01:23.708
- Marke bou!

01:23.792 --> 01:24.736
A tu tit.

01:25.225 --> 01:26.917
- Bak Danik.

01:27.000 --> 01:28.333
Ugh!
Ugh!

01:29.680 --> 01:31.210
Ah! Mmm.

01:31.290 --> 01:33.375
Quack'ın lat'ı.

01:33.470 --> 01:35.625
- Vay be, la ba li bi de Quack.

01:35.708 --> 01:41.542
Ah! Senin "Quack"n bir aptal.
Eh sata ta-ta?

01:41.625 --> 01:42.667
Eh Sinqa Tong.

01:42.750 --> 01:43.958
Zatick!
Blugh.

01:44.042 --> 01:44.917
Ta-ti!
- Zagh!

01:45.000 --> 01:47.375
Mourkats!
A ta-tara.

01:47.458 --> 01:48.583
Ugh...

01:48.670 --> 01:50.167
- Krinka!
Asita.

01:50.250 --> 01:51.583
Pour le King.
- Ma Dante.

01:51.667 --> 01:53.167
Zaldor!
Mal Pato.

01:53.250 --> 01:55.042
Philip Cots.
- Ma Toupit.

01:56.240 --> 02:00.766
Masiq et no et bleu.
Ta-ba ta-ba tou-be di?

02:01.292 --> 02:03.500
Arata, azit!

02:05.595 --> 02:06.958
Eh, oh! Oh!

02:07.042 --> 02:07.486
Oye.

02:09.128 --> 02:10.000
Waha aha.

02:10.080 --> 02:12.125
Hayır, blah, hayır.
Et ca?

02:12.210 --> 02:13.833
- Vay!
Evet!

02:13.917 --> 02:16.375
Za Bornak.
Bir de Paşa, bir kahkaha.

02:16.783 --> 02:18.917
Eh...
- Eh, bir sürü Shorplee!

02:19.000 --> 02:21.125
Vay.

02:21.208 --> 02:23.667
- Hey, ho, ho, ho. Ah. Quack!

02:23.750 --> 02:24.833
Quack!?

02:24.917 --> 02:26.833
Zaba goth.
A suba ti-ta.

02:26.917 --> 02:30.083
Ticka sack. Geri gitmek, bir düşünün.

02:35.110 --> 02:37.566
- "Banezinkat"?
Bada buta vouda.

02:37.670 --> 02:38.875
Too too.

03:07.417 --> 03:10.040
- Quack.
